snippet.title: Slipways - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Turn desolate planets into a vast trade empire. Hatch plans. Research game-breaking technologies. Still be done in time for lunch. Enjoy the endless possibilities of a space grand strategy game in 60 minutes flat. 

Slipways is a PC strategy game available Q2 2021.
Wishlist it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1264280/Slipways/
Discuss it here: https://discord.gg/qD97EDu
Track its development here: https://twitter.com/krajzeg
